description: Lists all the templates in the current Amazon QuickSight account.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the templates that you're listing.

nested_items.name: TemplateSummaryList
nested_items.description: A structure containing information about the templates in the list.

nested_items.name: TemplateId
nested_items.description: The ID of the template. This ID is unique per Amazon Web Services Region for each Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A display name for the template.

nested_items.name: LatestVersionNumber
nested_items.description: A structure containing a list of version numbers for the template summary.

nested_items.name: CreatedTime
nested_items.description: The last time that this template was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedTime
nested_items.description: The last time that this template was updated.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
